OL,3,CCalls to enforce heavy vehicle speed
OL,4,Climit law
OL,6,FCommittee member Deputy Andrew Taylor
OL,7,Fexplains: "I would like to certainly
OL,8,Fsee it discussed a bit more to
OL,9,Funderstand why it's not being enforced.
OL,11,F"I understand the resource
OL,12,Fimplications, but in my view, it could
OL,13,Frepresent a significant risk to the
OL,14,Fpublic."
OL,16,FDespite its quirks, some residents are
OL,17,Fin favour of heavier cars reducing
OL,18,Ftheir speeds on the island's roadways.
