OL,3,CCalls to enforce heavy vehicle speed
OL,4,Climit law
OL,6,FOne said that because of the island's
OL,7,Fnarrow roads, it "might be advisable
OL,8,Fthat (larger cars) stuck to something
OL,9,Fsmaller like 25mph.
OL,11,FAnother explains: "I think some of
OL,12,Fthese big vehicles just race along and
OL,13,Fif you're in a small vehicle and you
OL,14,Fcome in a crash with them, you're
OL,15,Fdefinitely going to come off worst."
