OL,6,FSome motor trade industry members
OL,7,Fbelieve the law is outdated and
OL,8,Funnecessary.
OL,10,FGuernsey garage owner Trevor Hockey
OL,11,Fexplains: "It's not a particularly
OL,12,Fwell thought out law, in my opinion as
OL,13,Fthere's no logic behind it.
OL,15,F"I can't see any reason for it being
OL,16,Fthere in the first place."
